1
00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:04,890
[Fated Hearts – The Fall of the Fierce General of Jinxiu]

2
00:00:05,030 --> 00:00:06,930
Who dares to be so noisy?

3
00:00:05,120 --> 00:00:07,920
[On-set of "Fated Hearts"] [Ning Fei arrives looking for someone]

4
00:00:06,930 --> 00:00:07,830
Feng Suige.

5
00:00:08,130 --> 00:00:09,230
One, two, three.

6
00:00:09,230 --> 00:00:10,360
Talk to you.

7
00:00:13,170 --> 00:00:13,760
Now… now.

8
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:17,360
[Learning needle removal from the Chinese medicine master]

9
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:14,400
Right now you're…

10
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,530
you're still poking inside.

11
00:00:15,530 --> 00:00:16,530
Then I pull it out—

12
00:00:17,630 --> 00:00:18,860
slowly.

13
00:00:19,530 --> 00:00:20,400
He told me to—

14
00:00:20,980 --> 00:00:21,680
don't.

15
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:22,310
A bit slower.

16
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:22,890
A little slower.

17
00:00:22,890 --> 00:00:23,290
Right.

18
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:25,430
[Always trust the professionals]

19
00:00:23,820 --> 00:00:24,120
Okay.

20
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:25,720
Let's do as the teacher says.

21
00:00:25,830 --> 00:00:26,960
He told me to do this.

22
00:00:28,900 --> 00:00:30,200
I guess this is it.

23
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,730
It's that kind of stress response.

24
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:32,299
Seeing them—

25
00:00:32,299 --> 00:00:33,930
reminds me of the past.

26
00:00:35,610 --> 00:00:36,820
Crazy.

27
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,730
Insane.

28
00:00:37,320 --> 00:00:38,380
[He's sick]

29
00:00:39,760 --> 00:00:41,080
A stress response.

30
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:43,460
Three, two, one—

31
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:44,450
Action!

32
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:48,190
[Wakes up after the needle is removed]

33
00:00:48,540 --> 00:00:51,710
[Xueying reporting a complaint]

34
00:00:48,610 --> 00:00:50,080
Do you know—

35
00:00:50,130 --> 00:00:51,860
there's someone named Ning Fei?

36
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:53,430
He claims to be your brother.

37
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:54,260
He just came looking for you,

38
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:56,090
but Feng Suige beat him up.

39
00:00:56,120 --> 00:00:57,500
He's pretty badly hurt.

40
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,690
[My brother was beaten!]

41
00:00:57,930 --> 00:00:58,500
Xueying,

42
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:00,970
go check on him for me.

43
00:01:00,820 --> 00:01:02,030
[Angrily questioning]

44
00:01:01,010 --> 00:01:01,870
I heard—

45
00:01:02,650 --> 00:01:04,379
you attacked my own kin once.

46
00:01:04,590 --> 00:01:05,390
Yes.

47
00:01:04,629 --> 00:01:06,550
[Readily admits it] [I, Feng Suige, own my actions]

48
00:01:06,950 --> 00:01:08,950
Why did you act without even asking?

49
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,130
Back then—

50
00:01:10,140 --> 00:01:11,060
[So angry he trips over his words]

51
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:13,030
What's going on?

52
00:01:13,030 --> 00:01:13,600
Sorry.

53
00:01:15,380 --> 00:01:16,560
You spared my life once,

54
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,900
and wanted me to cooperate,

55
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:19,860
so I could recover my memories sooner,

56
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:20,600
and help you uncover

57
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:22,130
who in Susha was the traitor.

58
00:01:22,130 --> 00:01:24,060
Then why stop me today, of all days?

59
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:27,670
[Finishes a long line in one breath]
